Subject: [PATCH] [UI][Opt] Hide reply background emoji

---
 Telegram/CMakeLists.txt                            |  2 ++
 .../history/view/history_view_reply.cpp            |  3 ++-
 .../settings/hide_reply_background_emoji.cpp       | 14 ++++++++++++++
 .../settings/hide_reply_background_emoji.h         |  5 +++++
 4 files changed, 23 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
 create mode 100644 Telegram/SourceFiles/yukigram/settings/hide_reply_background_emoji.cpp
